<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2">
<h2 id="Filmography">Filmography</h2>
<span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Karl_Popper&amp;action=edit&amp;section=25" title="Edit section: Filmography"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span>
</div>
<ul><li>
<i>Interview Karl Popper</i>, Open Universiteit, 1988.</li></ul>
